  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play over 100 games! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Downloadable wallpapers </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full soundtrack and music player </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make gameplay simpler with Help and Hint functions!</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>Collector's Edition</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Includes 8 extra themes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18 Downloadable Wallpapers </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music player </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 more collection room</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play So Much Stuff 3: Odds & Ends and dive into a delightful journey of sorting through an array of beautiful themes, clearing out a multitude of items and trinkets. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463730/extras/cd121d06a72394faaceff7571bf6a512.poster.avif?t=1729639798\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463730/extras/cd121d06a72394faaceff7571bf6a512.webm?t=1729639798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463730/extras/cd121d06a72394faaceff7571bf6a512.mp4?t=1729639798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this new set of beautifully created hidden object scenes, you will sort through unique odds & ends! Feel the satisfaction of organizing and decluttering! Sort through fun and interesting new themes and play a whole new set of mini-games!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463730/extras/57cd179fe7f920a74e2be449930fbcfd.poster.avif?t=1729639798\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463730/extras/57cd179fe7f920a74e2be449930fbcfd.webm?t=1729639798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463730/extras/57cd179fe7f920a74e2be449930fbcfd.mp4?t=1729639798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sit back, relax, and indulge in a diverse selection of engaging mini-games such as jigsaws, find the difference, and click to swaps!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play So Much Stuff 3: Odds & Ends and dive into a delightful journey of sorting through an array of beautiful themes, clearing out a multitude of items and trinkets. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463730/extras/cd121d06a72394faaceff7571bf6a512.poster.avif?t=1729639798\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463730/extras/cd121d06a72394faaceff7571bf6a512.webm?t=1729639798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463730/extras/cd121d06a72394faaceff7571bf6a512.mp4?t=1729639798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this new set of beautifully created hidden object scenes, you will sort through unique odds & ends! Feel the satisfaction of organizing and decluttering! Sort through fun and interesting new themes and play a whole new set of mini-games!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463730/extras/57cd179fe7f920a74e2be449930fbcfd.poster.avif?t=1729639798\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463730/extras/57cd179fe7f920a74e2be449930fbcfd.webm?t=1729639798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463730/extras/57cd179fe7f920a74e2be449930fbcfd.mp4?t=1729639798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sit back, relax, and indulge in a diverse selection of engaging mini-games such as jigsaws, find the difference, and click to swaps!</p>",
